Firefox
By: Shawn Wilkinson

Introduction
Firefox is a piece of software the allows you to surf the web.  This piece of software and others like it are known as web browsers, or more common browsers, because they say what they do. They browse the web. Firefox is in my opinion and many others the best browser. It has tabbed browsing, a password saver, search engine search, and many other features build in (these feature will be explained later). Firefox is also very secure, which is an important feature because of the many people out there that can take your information. In this tutorial you will learn how to use how to use firefox to the best of its capabilities. If you are a beginner or as, in the internet world a noob, you will learn a lot from this tutorial, or if you are a very skilled in computers you can learn tips and tricks on this browser (h4xx0r). 
