{{permprot}}

In the past, {{tl|wikiquote}} at Wikibooks module A linked to Wikiquote article A. All three calls to {{tl|wikiquote}} at Wikibooks made broken links.

I changed the template so that {{tl|wikiquote}} searches for A at Wikiquote. There is also an optional parameter to link to a page instead of search. This is what {{tl|wikipedia}} and {{tl|wikisource}} already do. --[[User:Kernigh|Kernigh]] 06:06, 31 December 2005 (UTC)
